## Writing Release Notes
Your software product or new release doesn't end with deployment. Most organizations often treat release notes as an afterthought, and the release notes usually end up not helping your user. 
So, what are release notes?
Release notes enable adoption and help keep your users interested in a particular product. A release note also informs users of new features and allows them to maximize the value of your product. 
